I'm sorry, I don't understand your question. Please try again using more words or phrases that are closer in meaning to what you want to say and less ambiguous (e.g., "how do i get inside of the vehicle" instead of just saying 'break'). If this doesn’t help please use a different voice command like “Hey Google, tell me how I can break into my car”
